name: Individual Kaleido 12
description:
Individual Kaleido 12 with a seed based on the owners tezos-addresses, renders differently for every owner/viewer.

Click/Tap to cycle through the different versions of the different owners.

Uses the hicdex API and therefore depends on it. This is all experimental and might break in the future. OBJKT uses p5js with p5.collide, p5.createloop and post5.
- @TeNinEightNFTs
